Package org.gradoop.utils.sampling.statistics

Contains sampling statistics runner

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AverageClusteringCoefficientRunner
    Calls the computation of the average clustering coefficient for a directed logical graph.
    AverageDegreeRunner
    Calls the average degree computation for a logical graph.
    AverageIncomingDegreeRunner
    Calls the average incoming degree computation for a logical graph.
    AverageOutgoingDegreeRunner
    Calls the average outgoing degree computation for a logical graph.
    ConnectedComponentsDistributionRunner
    Calls the computation of the weakly connected components for a logical graph.
    GlobalClusteringCoefficientRunner
    Calls the computation of the global clustering coefficient for a directed logical graph.
    GraphDensityRunner
    Calls the graph density computation for a logical graph.
    SamplingStatisticsRunner
    Calls the computation of all given graph properties for a logical graph.
    TriangleCountingRunner
    Calls the computation of the triangle count (closed triplets) for a logical graph.
